# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #            tanh (epoch>=20 ngay tß╗ź ─Ĺß║žu).

# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #   FIX-T-B  [HIGH] evaluate_full_val_ade() cache raw_ctx: kh├┤ng gß╗Źi
# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #            model.net._context() 2 lß║žn cho c├╣ng mß╗Öt batch.
# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #            T├şch hß╗úp compute_sr_ade() v├áo v├▓ng lß║Ěp ch├şnh.

# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #   FIX-T-C  [HIGH] Phase 1 freeze: freeze ctx_fc1 v├á ctx_ln c├╣ng vß╗Ťi
# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #            backbone. L├Ż do: raw_ctx tß╗ź frozen encoder Ôćĺ chß║ąt lĂ░ß╗úng k├ęm
# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #            Ôćĺ ShortRangeHead hß╗Źc tr├¬n noise nß║┐u ctx_fc1 kh├┤ng frozen.

# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #   FIX-T-D  [MEDIUM] short_range_weight schedule: kh├┤ng cß║žn scale cß╗▒c
# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #            cao (12.0) v├Č short_range_regression_loss ─Ĺ├ú normalize ─Ĺ├║ng
# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #            (─ĹĂín vß╗ő km thß╗▒c, kh├┤ng chia th├¬m HUBER_DELTA nß╗»a).
# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #            Schedule mß╗Ťi: 5.0 Ôćĺ 3.0 Ôćĺ 2.0.

# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #   FIX-T-E  [MEDIUM] Bridge loss weight: k├şch hoß║ít tß╗ź epoch 10 sau khi
# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #            cß║ú SR v├á FM ─Ĺ├ú c├│ prediction c├│ ngh─ęa. ep 0-9: 0.0, sau: 0.5.

