# # # # # # # # # KEY CHANGES vs v46:
# # # # # # # # #   1. Loss v50: DPE(v50_weights) + 0.03*MSE + 0.05*speed + 0.01*accel
# # # # # # # # #                + 0.15*heading + 0.30*vel_reg + 0.25*endpoint
# # # # # # # # #   2. STEP_WEIGHTS_V50: [1,1,1,1.5,2,2.5,3,4,5,6,7,10] ÔÇö 72h = 10x
# # # # # # # # #   3. Sigma schedule: 0.15Ôćĺ0.04 tß╗ź ep2 (nhanh hĂín v46)
# # # # # # # # #   4. Inference v50: speed-sweep ensemble (7 scales ├Ś 50 members)
# # # # # # # # #   5. Log th├¬m: vel_reg, endpoint, heading

# # # # # # # # # MONITOR:
# # # # # # # # #   - vel_reg phß║úi giß║úm li├¬n tß╗ąc: ep0~2.0, ep10~0.5, ep20~0.3
# # # # # # # # #   - endpoint phß║úi < 1.0 ß╗č ep10
# # # # # # # # #   - heading phß║úi < 0.3 ß╗č ep15
# # # # # # # # #   - 72h phß║úi < 350 ß╗č ep15, < 300 ß╗č ep30
# # # # # # # # #   - ATE phß║úi < 150 ß╗č ep20, < 80 ß╗č ep40

# # # # # # # # # Nß║żU vel_reg kh├┤ng giß║úm sau ep5: t─âng weight 0.30Ôćĺ0.40 trong patch
