# # #   Save 5 types of checkpoints SEPARATELY (avoid EMA-good-but-RAW-bad issue):
# # #     1. best_composite.pth ÔÇö Best composite score (EMA-or-RAW, like v59)
# # #     2. best_raw.pth       ÔÇö Best RAW (no-EMA) full-val score [NEW]
